The paper introduces a new approach to deep learning models, which involves genetic-evolutionary learning strategy to build a group of unit models. This approach is significantly different from the well-known representation learning models with extremely deep structures. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY).
